	<!-- message -->
	<p>Well I play on a blue server and this is what I know. PVP is always consential I believe on a blue servers. Red servers you cannot kill people of your side, only people of the other team. <br />
<br />
Not sure on the penalty, but the death penalty in general is gear degredation which can get a bit expensive. <br />
<br />
Someone on a red server would have to give you more of that.</p>
	
	
	
