	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>You can attack anyone on the opposing faction at any time on a PvP server.  A level 20 human mage jumped my level 18 shaman today in the barrens (horde territory).  Luckily I still kicked his ass, well okay I beat him with 20 hp left!  Shamans rule at PvP.<br />
<br />
Anyways the penalty for dying is the same as a on PvP death at this point, not sure if they are changing it.  You lose 10% of your items durability per death.  100% if you need to use the spirit healer person.<br />
<br />
Im Walruss on Test 32 btw, if anyone plays there, hit me up.</p>
	
	
	
