	<!-- message -->
	<p>Guys it really is simple. On a pvp server, the same exact rules apply in your home territories, you cannot be ganked unless you attack first.<br />
<br />
If you are in contested territory(vast majority of level 20-60 zones), anyone can attack anyone of the opposing faction.<br />
<br />
If you are in enemy territory, anyone can attack you.<br />
<br />
it is not "free for all", you cannot be killed in the barrens unless you attack somone first, and you cannot be slaughtered as a newbie, period.<br />
<br />
Mill</p>
	
	
	
